# 0.8.11 — skip the onnxruntime-node CUDA GPU download in its postinstall
# (linux-x64 only; never used — browser app → onnxruntime-web, CPU binaries
# bundled; api.nuget.org times out on CI runners). Belt-and-braces with the
# ONNXRUNTIME_NODE_INSTALL=skip env set in ci-test.yml and frontend/Dockerfile.
onnxruntime-node-install=skip
